other_tests.findings: Fasting plasma glucose of 102 mg/dl indicating mild impaired fasting glucose (IFG); 1-hour and 2-hour serum glucose values were normal.
other_tests.changes_over_time: In 2018, a second OGTT was normal with no sign of IFG, and an elevated insulin level was noted at the 1-hour time point.

other_tests.findings: 1-hour serum glucose of 241 mg/dl and a 2-hour value of 204 mg/dl diagnostic of Type 2 diabetes.
